{"tid":569862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"400幾萬買170呎納米樓　14親友拜年逼爆無碇企　樓主：我好想喊","createTime":"2018-02-23T06:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T19:22:19.000Z","uid":10958,"like":145,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":150,"replies":[{"pid":"d954d8eba83b230bc5d61e620132a5be09342e9b","tid":569862,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>400幾萬買170呎納米樓　14親友拜年逼爆無碇企　樓主：我好想喊<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/161990/thumbnail/407c79d47f0600229c53c1decfc3a38d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F161990%2Fthumbnail%2F407c79d47f0600229c53c1decfc3a38d.jpg&h=ef4e2997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土地問題困擾港人多時，不少新婚夫婦因沒法買樓而被迫「分居」，但買到面積極小的「納米樓」亦不好過！一名以400多萬元購得實用面積僅170呎納米樓的男網民，日前在香港討論區分享納米樓業主悲歌，指大年初一足足有14名親友登門拜年，結果一半人需要站着，而煎煮糕點時，全屋即充斥油煙味，過程令樓主夫婦十分尷尬，事後吵大鑊，樓主大呼：「我好想喊，點解要買呢d（啲）垃圾納米樓！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226506/xlarge/d9d3766fe0f7b6ed82026cf546760f12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226506%2Fxlarge%2Fd9d3766fe0f7b6ed82026cf546760f12.jpg&h=5d0eca48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226513/xlarge/2b27ebd534ccaf263c78013b0e58ef3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226513%2Fxlarge%2F2b27ebd534ccaf263c78013b0e58ef3d.jpg&h=8e311365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226510/xlarge/cc6a3505018d411d83dbc3b81aab3500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226510%2Fxlarge%2Fcc6a3505018d411d83dbc3b81aab3500.jpg&h=65d81c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226511/xlarge/955a8f728e4a6d10d86fd36152b101a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226511%2Fxlarge%2F955a8f728e4a6d10d86fd36152b101a2.jpg&h=b86432b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226512/xlarge/9ea9cb6744795c22e0566f53042af137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226512%2Fxlarge%2F9ea9cb6744795c22e0566f53042af137.jpg&h=fafaa651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該名網民在大年初二（17日）於香港討論區以「唉，昨日初一，就因為間納米樓同老婆嘈交嘈左（咗）鑊金」為題發文，指於年初一上午與妻子到朋友家拜年，朋友的家位於九龍站附近，「有六七百實呎，我地一行十幾人去都坐得好鬆動」。到了下午，妻子的同事便轉到他們家拜年，事情即急轉直下。<br />\n<br />\n樓主形容其寓所是「實呎得百七呎」的納米樓，所以當時已經心想「死梗」，「我老婆唔知係想show off我地窩居既（嘅）靚lobby定clubhouse，call齊14人來！無錯，係14人！」。<br />\n<br />\n要來的始終要來，樓主在大堂迎接妻子的同事，最初大家都十分開心，向雙方說恭喜的說話，「但一入到屋，一眼睇哂（晒），14個人有一半係要企」，部分人更坐在床上，樓主感到十分失禮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226813/xlarge/711f9d9013503a014a91892ad955e554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226813%2Fxlarge%2F711f9d9013503a014a91892ad955e554.jpg&h=827e6aae&s={SIZE}\" />[img][/img]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">納米樓面積有限，沒有太多空間可以使用。圖為示意圖片。（資料圖片）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n沒有最難堪，只有更難堪。一會兒後，由於有小朋友表示肚餓，樓主便在單位內的開放式廚房煎煮新年糕點，全屋立即充斥油煙味，其間「有個男同事唔知有心定真係病，係到（喺度）狂咳」，使樓主夫婦感到更加尷尬，各人多坐一會兒便離開。樓主最後在帖文大呼：「我好想喊，點解要買呢d（啲）垃圾納米樓！」，其妻子亦向他表示不滿，向他發出埋怨。<br />\n<br />\n樓主其後再在貼文回覆，指自己因事件失眠了一整晚，「不斷反思，花成四百幾萬，買間垃圾納米樓，唔可以招呼朋友，唔可以生小朋友，唔可以下廚，咁既（嘅）樓要來把X？」。有網民留言指「買納米唔一定係錯，最錯既係仲要show off」，又說住納米樓不邀請朋友作客是常識。有心更鼓勵樓主「畀啲心機換大屋」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226683/xlarge/fff0dc261f116ee17a2627c53a0d06f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226683%2Fxlarge%2Ffff0dc261f116ee17a2627c53a0d06f4.jpg&h=ef5334b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226678/xlarge/dd995969ae4b577fd604b714a1ea037d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226678%2Fxlarge%2Fdd995969ae4b577fd604b714a1ea037d.jpg&h=fd39b936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226681/xlarge/8bc93188a0c911d80085c35fda44cd3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226681%2Fxlarge%2F8bc93188a0c911d80085c35fda44cd3a.jpg&h=8c427edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226679/xlarge/2585584f91ed830c03b6be7817924733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226679%2Fxlarge%2F2585584f91ed830c03b6be7817924733.jpg&h=72bb3839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226680/xlarge/56b0a936574ca4c804902d4ffd97bcca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226680%2Fxlarge%2F56b0a936574ca4c804902d4ffd97bcca.jpg&h=8e2d64a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226685/xlarge/fcee492192992c48e745da4ba9bfb004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226685%2Fxlarge%2Ffcee492192992c48e745da4ba9bfb004.jpg&h=bd058c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226686/xlarge/4db5e98f614ee9b0cab5052dedbbe1e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226686%2Fxlarge%2F4db5e98f614ee9b0cab5052dedbbe1e1.jpg&h=be1d65e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226682/xlarge/8045c55e1a3c8d274efd0c225d9ae774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226682%2Fxlarge%2F8045c55e1a3c8d274efd0c225d9ae774.jpg&h=a859becd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/161990?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F161990%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=czLhboHiFNV%2BMEKCeGGQ0zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0432fcf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/161990?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"c1f3375b4d5dac0227c6773f569f4d389997566a","tid":569862,"uid":108236,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5318375d89bf0aa66159ac01621f6cca1bd0db51","tid":569862,"uid":65406,"like":100,"dislike":1,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:08:16.000Z","msg":"發展商:錢已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c959ac6f50a93fe7660dd190d4f8b6389688b61","tid":569862,"uid":97551,"like":317,"dislike":1,"score":316,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 買果陣就預左啦<br />\n<br />\n發展商真仆街 起到咁撚細 仲要賣到咁撚貴"},{"pid":"660281c2c73570afb411afd82494401ed86e7ea3","tid":569862,"uid":6211,"like":254,"dislike":3,"score":251,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:10:25.000Z","msg":"買之前已經知係咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫人黎之前已經知係咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecae478e98d9888c437484c4ba51820947d54038","tid":569862,"uid":128568,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"HK01"},{"pid":"28c559a3b917c4b1ec5a54ab8c46ad63363b7ea0","tid":569862,"uid":8883,"like":371,"dislike":3,"score":368,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"個老婆又要請咁多人上黎<br />\n失禮完怨番個老公轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4269118637967c66a63c2fe11482badd3